Business Brief -- Sulcus Computer Corp.:
   Agreement on Acquisition
   Of Private Firm Is Reached
Squirrel, a producer of touch-screen point-of-sale
technology, currently has more than 1,800 customers on four
continents, including the Hilton International hotel chain
and ChiChi's Restaurants. Revenue exceeds $5 million
annually. Sulcus makes automated systems for the lodging,
legal and real estate markets.